// a dark rounded square). Used wherever the mark sits beside the "Partwright"
// wordmark (landing hero, toolbar, catalog, what's-new, about modal); the tile
// container keeps it from reading as the leading "P" of the word. Keep this in
// sync with public/favicon.svg / public/og-image.svg (hand-duplicated rasters).
