// Geometry: an oblique-projection voxel P (cube grid, lit top→front→side),
// generated by .plans/build-voxel-sets.mjs. Coordinates are in the inner
// 0–64 voxel space, placed inside the 104×104 tile via translate(4 6) scale(1.5).

